# Module Size and Design

- Target <= 250 lines per file; avoid > 400 lines without explicit justification.
- Target <= 40 lines per function where practical.
- Apply single responsibility per function/module.
- Extract helpers/components/hooks when complexity grows.
- Prefer clear, domain-oriented naming over generic utility naming.
- Reduce duplication instead of copying logic across files.
